00:03:47.472 --> 00:03:48.806
<v Regina>Absolutely.</v>

92
00:03:48.806 --> 00:03:53.806
Let's talk about your definition of the difference between

93
00:03:53.830 --> 00:03:55.461
the mind and the brain,

94
00:03:55.461 --> 00:04:00.165
